1. On *razmišlja* o tome šta bi mogao da uradi. (He is *thinking* about what he could do.)
2. Razmišljao sam o tom problemu celo popodne. (*I was thinking* about that problem all afternoon.)
3. Ti *razmišljaš* previše, opusti se malo. (You *think* too much, relax a bit.)
4. Kada *razmišljate* o kupovini novog auta, imajte na umu troškove održavanja. (When you *think* about buying a new car, keep in mind maintenance costs.)
5. Ona *razmišlja* da promeni karijeru i postane frizerka. (She is *thinking* about changing her career and becoming a hairdresser.)
6. *Razmišljam* da sutra odem na trčanje u park. (*I'm thinking* about going for a run in the park tomorrow.)
7. Kada sam *razmišljao* o svojim snovima, nikada nisam mislio da ću uspeti da ih ostvarim. (When I *thought* about my dreams, I never thought I would be able to achieve them.)
8. Ne znam o čemu *razmišljaš*, ali vidim da si zabrinut. (I don't know what you're *thinking* about, but I can see you're worried.)
9. On *razmišlja* da prestane da puši i počne da vežba. (He is *thinking* about quitting smoking and starting to exercise.)
10. *Razmišljajte* o tome šta biste mogli da uradite da biste bili srećniji. (*Think* about what you could do to be happier.)